  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸바리 박스, 패키지 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0b6a1a7-47e7-4c85-b163-fe0199becb0a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d64c98f7-c1f1-4e8b-aa78-8093b8e499d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d64c98f7-c1f1-4e8b-aa78-8093b8e499d9\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDJfMjM4/MDAxNzU0MTA2Nzc5Nzcx.hVNOQHaE4mlclIEVNQG4rTcPy6v2IBpoPPPWa2ayVZwg.gqoea9zcWjr0NDQFqARr9FEhnGI51wjUjlT86IOdqKUg.PNG/SE-d64c98f7-c1f1-4e8b-aa78-8093b8e499d9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDJfMjM4/MDAxNzU0MTA2Nzc5Nzcx.hVNOQHaE4mlclIEVNQG4rTcPy6v2IBpoPPPWa2ayVZwg.gqoea9zcWjr0NDQFqARr9FEhnGI51wjUjlT86IOdqKUg.PNG/SE-d64c98f7-c1f1-4e8b-aa78-8093b8e499d9.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">싸바리 박스에서 가장 중요한 것은 무엇?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">싸바리 박스 제작 시 가장 중요한 것이 무엇일까요? 가격, 납기, 퀄리티, 서비스 중에 여러분은 무엇이라고 생각하십니까?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a87a707-19a5-478a-ad6c-74aa9731803f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c201bc1f-f2cf-4097-af79-4b852f211877\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28925a6d-eddf-4abc-b67b-8ef89a7cf2b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8d57ba88-861b-442f-82aa-e3e363db0d04\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 이 4가지 요소는 다 중요합니다. 하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-50a453c2-6137-4ccb-aefb-8f6f8a93d5f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>퀄리티를 가장 중요하게 생각</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d4989627-3fed-47c0-bb68-c15936163732\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다. 가격만을 고집하는 고객님은 사실상 저희와 맞지 않을 수 있습니다. 물론 저희가 가격을 무시하고 엄청난 바가지(?) 가격을 제시하지는 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f179bff-48b9-4156-9535-b61998044265\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3a6f1fb-c1f8-4ef9-848b-f852bb4f8f54\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c8c15603-789d-4dad-95c0-21429fc48436\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2cc5ba95-345a-4453-837d-b1a3e4feab32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 가격비딩을 위한 경쟁을 하지 않는다고 말씀드립니다. 가격을 무시하지는 않지만 낮은 가격으로만 경쟁하지 않는다는 뜻입니다. 특히 싸바리 박스의 경우 퀄리티가 가장 중요합니다. 여러 가지 부분을 감안하고 고려하려 제안 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34b4cd4a-a5f1-4c1e-8e46-a1d4df6decec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e31140ff-91af-47b4-a7d7-29bff26b247f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d7fef858-6ea6-4cd1-990b-d2d464cc02e3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-baece8af-ba3f-4c82-8b11-4a97de01291d\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>제품의 퀄리티를 높이는 방법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79d2b386-38bf-4818-9755-0d7371625257\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4fc2ac16-ae5e-46fc-b91a-89269a7f736b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님께서는 퀄리티를 높이기 위한 방법은 무엇이라고 생각하시나요? 종이의 질? 최신 인쇄기? 경력이 많은 인쇄 기장? 물론 이 부분은 다 중요합니다만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2ffad372-2e71-46f8-894f-dea8abca3464\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>고객과의 끊임없는 소통</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0da64883-7380-4b78-b1e9-59fbc13c829c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이라고 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-add9a136-a3aa-4804-9d79-915d7d99f916\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81f48b91-3b79-45d2-b0d1-15e67b4e43c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4f0092d-9154-4a8e-8a88-27317a4d03fb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ee04dddb-60b6-4270-b2b2-a800500705df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">실시간(?)으로 제작되는 과정을 사진이나 동영상을 찍어서 고객과 소통하는 것이 가장 중요하다고 생각합니다. 이런 소통만이 사고를 없애고 퀄리티를 직접 확인하는 과정이라고 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e2982a4-13aa-4135-a0f7-0ab1f35a2092\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1012286-c348-411e-8bb0-e266507b6cae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8aaaef3d-ce4b-4d35-afe3-e1c0e1f4df85\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d785c6eb-de43-4668-ad40-62bfede235b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8aa3be0d-7cbe-466c-bafd-522468f36912\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>확인 또 확인이 가장 중요한 핵심</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8bbb5c97-9716-45bf-97a0-49d40dd4dcbc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 방심하면 사고 납니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-e2d81de7-11d0-470f-af46-323a4d7f8917\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-64376f7f-a93d-43cc-a02e-dc0ba630f91c\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDJfODUg/MDAxNzU0MTA5MDkxMzc0.Uo0BWVH3y6bvONL6qCqQUYJWGLGHRtT1965mK5o6S1og.mwYeAzDkb0hT_vP4VGsnilFW9fQWqcTGxT14y2U3wuYg.JPEG/SE-64376f7f-a93d-43cc-a02e-dc0ba630f91c.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2250\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDJfODUg/MDAxNzU0MTA5MDkxMzc0.Uo0BWVH3y6bvONL6qCqQUYJWGLGHRtT1965mK5o6S1og.mwYeAzDkb0hT_vP4VGsnilFW9fQWqcTGxT14y2U3wuYg.JPEG/SE-64376f7f-a93d-43cc-a02e-dc0ba630f91c.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">